&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is a clear growth platform. With the right results, the natural growth path is Senior Manager or Director of Data, with broader scope across analytics, ML platform, and AI.&lt;/p&gt;
