&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ShipMonk&lt;/strong&gt; | Pittston, Pennsylvania | Full-time | On-site&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Department Ownership &amp;amp; Scope&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ShipMonk is seeking an Operations Supervisor to directly manage daily fulfillment operations and lead a team of 25–30 fulfillment associates at our Pittston, PA facility. Across our network of 12+ global fulfillment centers, we execute daily high-volume e-commerce fulfillment for over 1,500 brands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an operational optimization role. Rather than executing a static, corporate-mandated playbook, you will directly influence, test, and implement standard operating procedures (SOPs) to reduce cycle times, minimize travel waste, and eliminate quality defects on the floor.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Growth Trajectory&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We prioritize internal progression based on measurable output and team development metrics. Supervisors who meet throughput targets and successfully cross-train their teams step directly into Senior Supervisor and Warehouse Manager tracks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Offer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unlimited Paid Time Off (PTO)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Comprehensive Medical, Dental, and Vision Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monthly Performance Bonus Structure&lt;/strong&gt; tied directly to department KPI achievements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Internal Promotion Pathways&lt;/strong&gt; backed by active leadership development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities &amp;amp; Daily Deliverables&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shift Optimization:&lt;/strong&gt; Launch daily shifts with structured team huddles to allocate labor, establish production targets, clear backlogs, and enforce safety protocols.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real-Time KPI Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Monitor and adjust intra-day labor allocation to meet or exceed throughput, units per hour (UPH), accuracy, and safety benchmarks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Floor Coaching:&lt;/strong&gt; Conduct active, real-time performance coaching on the floor to improve individual associate metrics and accelerate onboarding ramp times.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Coordination:&lt;/strong&gt; Resolve cross-department bottlenecks immediately to maintain seamless hand-offs between receiving, picking, packing, and shipping.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Continuous Improvement (CI):&lt;/strong&gt; Analyze daily shift data to identify root causes of operational friction, propose targeted process modifications, and execute approved adjustments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Facility Compliance:&lt;/strong&gt; Maintain strict adherence to OSHA safety regulations, equipment maintenance schedules, and 5S cleanliness standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
